# CHANGELOG.md is generated by changesets/action and uses 2-space-indented
# changeset entries that prettier reformats incompatibly with markdownlint
# (prettier strips MD022 blank lines after headings inside the indented
# blocks). Without this exclusion, the pre-commit hook ping-pongs:
# markdownlint --fix adds blank lines, prettier --write removes them — the
# net result is that staged content gets reverted to HEAD on commit and
# the file lands as an empty diff. See ASW-94 PR #6 thread.
CHANGELOG.md
